summary:
Corporate Manager with substantial in-house business experience focused on Rugged/Military programs that include: Dutch and Canadian Navy applications as ship certification and sonar/radar systems. Dutch and UK Airforce applications related to: F-16 MLU, JSF, Chinook maintenance and Apache. Further more civil applications with ESA, BEA, Airbus and UAV programs.
Lately Imaging systems, High Definition format and High Speed Camera are rapidly gaining recognition.
Languages include: English, German, French, Dutch, Russian and Frisian :).

Specialties: Company Management. People Management, Competitive Analysis, Acquisition, Technical Support and Follow-up.
